OL,3,CLocal elections: How could the West
OL,4,CMidlands change after the 7th May?
OL,6,FThis week's elections in the West
OL,7,FMidlands are going to be significant,
OL,8,Fwith huge losses expected for the
OL,9,Ftraditional powerhouse parties, Labour
OL,10,Fand the Conservatives.
OL,12,FWith the turnout likely to be low and
OL,13,Fthe vote split many ways, each seat
OL,14,Fcould only take a few votes to change
OL,15,Fhands.
OL,17,FWith no party dominating in the polls,
OL,18,Fthe questions after the dust settles
OL,19,Fwill likely be about coalition and
OL,20,Fcompromise.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
